<module>
    <h>còmhla</h>
    <p><g>còmhla</g>
        <en>together</en> is an <a href="?xx=adverbs/adverbs">adverb</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>nouns</h>
        <module id="cuu">
            <h>cù</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=cuu">cù</a> còmhla ri ...</g> <en>a dog together with ...</en> –
                <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an cù còmhla ri Calum anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>The dog is along with Calum in the field today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 15</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil an cù? Tha e còmhla ri Calum.</gd>
                        <tr>Where is the dog? It is with Calum.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 19–20</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <module id="cat">
                <h>cat</h>
                <p><g><a href="?gd=cat">cat</a> còmhla ri ...</g> <en>a cat together with ...</en> –
                    <xl>
                        <li>
                            <gd>Tha an cat anns an taigh còmhla ri Seònaid.</gd>
                            <tr>The cat is in the house along with Janet.</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                        </li>
                    </xl>
                </p>
            </module>
        </module>
    </section>



