    <section>
        <h>verbs</h>
        <module id="cluich">
            <h>cluich</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=cluich">cluich</a> còmhla</g>
                <en>plays together</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an cat a’ cluich còmhla ri Seònaid air an làr?</gd>
                        <tr>Is the cat playing with Janet on the floor?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Nach robh Calum agus Màiri a’ cluich còmhla ris a’ chù? Cha robh, bha
                            iad anns a’ bhaile.</gd>
                        <tr>Weren’t Malcolm and Mary playing with the dog? No, they weren’t, they
                            were in the town.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21 [230]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>


